textAfterTable: Click Image to Enlarge Highlights: This active ship features an outdoor jogging track, full service spa, outdoor and indoor pool and six whirlpools. The stunning, two-tiered dining room serves up a wide array of delicious cuisine including fresh seafood, choice cuts of beef and sinful deserts. Rain or shine lay out poolside in the stunning Solarium that features a retractable roof. Past guests loved the ships friendly staff, onboard entertainment and beautiful public areas. Your Package Includes: Your package includes shipboard accommodations, ocean transportation, fabulous entertainment and daily activities, on-board meals and some beverages, port charges and more. It does not include shore excursions, personal expenses, gratuities, or alcoholic beverages. Government fees and taxes are not included.
